2026-05-14T00:34:28.9859288Z 21    <!--
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9859632Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9859811Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9860130Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9860419Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9860723Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9861227Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9861532Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9861842Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9862374Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9862647Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9862798Z 32    -->
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9863183Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
