2026-05-14T00:34:28.9878264Z 47        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9878589Z 48        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-14T00:34:28.9878869Z 49        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
